Burnoff is a Tentacle using power that will remove
the toxins that are caused by using heals. Each
tentacle assigned to removal will increase the
chances per round of toxins being lessened. The
tenticles will reverse and spread out into the body
and bloodstream of the user, and there do its work.

Cost: 15 Sps and 5 mp, with a constant drain on Hps.
Skill Level: Control 3

